h1.  Timer Trigger

h2. Purpose

This trigger provides a cron-like feature to periodically execute this project.

h2. Description

Usage:
{code}
triggers {
    timer {
        spec '5 * * * *'
    }
}
{code}

Required arguments:

@spec@: This field follows the syntax of cron (with minor differences). Specifically, each line consists of 5 fields separated by TAB or whitespace: